The main purpose of this project is to provide an API for movies.

On the load of if, it reads a CSV with a movie list and save in a memory database (H2).

The api provide endpoints to:

1 - List all movies
2 - Insert a new movie
3 - Deleta a movie
4 - Get which Producers have receive awards with a bigger period between them
5 - Get which Producers have receive awards with a shoter period between them

### Getting started with the project

mvn clean install -DskipTests
mvn spring-boot:run

### Examples to consume the API

File: movies.http

### Running tests

mvn clean install -DskipTests
mvn test
